snippet.title: Overthrown - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Overthrown is coming to Steam Early Access and Game Preview for Xbox Series X/S and PC on December 5! 
Available day one with Xbox Game Pass.

Lift and throw anything as you build and manage your kingdom in this chaotic city builder with up-to 6-player co-op. 
Harness the power of your soul-stealing crown to partake in anime-style combat, farm the land, gather resources and much more.

Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1133500/Overthrown/
